# Forming the Iron Front

Our rival fascists are gaining in strength, as shown by their recent election results and their violent presence in the streets. Their version of fascism threatens to eclipse our own.

While the brave RFB fighters are taking the fight to the Nazis, many in our party are calling for discussion of the concept of plan for addressing them. The "neorevisionist" faction, led by feckless opportunists like Carlo Mierendorff and Julius Leber, have formed specifically around this cause. But many in all factions of the party are making scared noises.

- @not_a_big_deal: The Nazis' moment will pass. Let's not get too hasty.
- @economic_crisis
- @major_crisis: Someone must do something to confront the Nazis.
- @iron_front


@not_a_big_deal
