The Nazis are one of the foremost threats to our cherished status quo. However, we are still formulating the draft version of an idea for a strategy to have a truly robust conversation about them, and still trying to build up consensus within our disarrayed excuse for a party. For now, we shall do our best to ignore their existence.

@iron_front
title: Form the Iron Front!
subtitle: The Iron Front consists of the SPD, the trade unions, and the Reichsbanner.
